{"tid":2384103,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大肚婆細路哥聯盟 - 陳也","createTime":"2021-01-28T10:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T10:43:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2daf93510531c58f989f40943e712753111d5f5f","tid":2384103,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210128/DJMMNY6G45BENCKP4SILTDHFVQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210128%2FDJMMNY6G45BENCKP4SILTDHFVQ%2F&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=de2f6dbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210128%2FDJMMNY6G45BENCKP4SILTDHFVQ%2F&h=b42d7881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210128/DJMMNY6G45BENCKP4SILTDHFVQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n大肚婆細路哥聯盟 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3Ifc0IveRoioP5XgT9HXZY0g3YI=/1249x719/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5GHIYHNWZ5ALZBC7OTNHFB7TPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3Ifc0IveRoioP5XgT9HXZY0g3YI%3D%2F1249x719%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5GHIYHNWZ5ALZBC7OTNHFB7TPY.png&h=89fa795b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有最衰，只有更衰。心諗七秒就好，糾纏太耐，好易被這個政府迫到發癲。大家一早講好嘛，見字飲水，留有用之軀，同佢鬥長命！<br />\n<br />\n好彩有人沖喜，堅如長毛浪人，竟然與女戰友拉埋天窗，朋友們嘩嘩聲一地眼鏡碎片，真係恭喜佢地呀。這邊岑敖暉大個仔，與同齡女友甜蜜簽字，好人好事，一生幸福。<br />\n<br />\n困在佐敦封城區內的七歲尼籍小孩，見到對面賓館開房緊貼報道的記者，站在窗前鬼馬晒Pepe公仔，戴蜘蛛俠面罩任影，最後手放頭頂做出心形手勢。小男孩胖胖的，落街不會被差佬罵「死肥仔」吧，尼籍男孩假如姓黎，就難講了。比他大些少、11歲的天水圍關注組主席王繼祖，落區勸喻大媽舞者將音響收細，離罩大叔眼見罵大肚婆「死肥婆」反綁雙手都得囉，動粗兼大罵王繼祖「如果你係我個孫，我斬死你呀！」大叔高尚情操成咁，。。。。。。。。。。"}]}